{"tid":1418932,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭出許sir 我地其實都可以學下","createTime":"2019-08-05T21:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:14:46.000Z","uid":43311,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e677dcf5b05eef7d483bb567ad1425587d74aa93","tid":1418932,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:52:40.000Z","msg":"林鄭特登開個記者會講每日有個記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用返雨革冷處理果招每日4點鐘許sir<br />\n日日就係無限俾佢砌生肉<br />\n全部任佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我地唔學佢每日6點鐘陳生<br />\n講返啲黑警點濫權<br />\n例如show下啲彈頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再每次宣讀我地嘅訴求及聲明<br />\n而且有咩活動都可以公佈<br />\n例如今日有人話唔知85罷工<br />\n開哂記招就無得懶唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港依然有好多人好似咩都唔知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢開一次記者會我地又跟住開<br />\n誰是誰非 要明嘅人就會明<br />\n而且透過媒體發表可以更廣泛傳遞訊息<br />\n<br />\n最後問題只係邊個人願意做代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03299f1a530ecc7e786850507cac0704369dc87a","tid":1418932,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:55:15.000Z","msg":"8月6  11：00 會有第一次民間記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414615</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8593777ba645b235d2363a6c60fbb2ba0a08539","tid":1418932,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:24:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5318a22f1adf881026028ba8d22251bd27d1afc0","tid":1418932,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:21:44.000Z","msg":"建議：不如搵杜汶澤 何韻詩搞民間記者會啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1413045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1413045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc0c65a649499d45db56adf427cf8b37ef8453a5","tid":1418932,"uid":242702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"記住 忘記小敵人 唔好畀每日許sir政治娛樂化 畀人模糊焦點 2014年就係每日許sir後 啲人成日笑佢講錯嘢 加上此後警察態度軟化 啲人對啲狗仲有一絲希望 最後令成個運動玩完"}]}